dc_title_s: Raccoon Creek, New Jersey from Swedesboro to Springer's Wharf
dc_description_s: Map 1: Raccoon Creek from Molonox Shoal to Swedesboro. |Map shows Raccoon Creek with soundings, the 7 foot curve and 4 foot curve, the mean low water line, proposed improvements and jetty. There is a diagram of the New Highway Draw Bridge, a detail of survey near the new highway draw bridge, and a locality sketch. |Map 2: Raccoon Creek from Springer's Bar to Shorn's Wharf. |Map shows Raccoon Creek with soundings and some wharfs along the creek. |Map 3: Raccoon Creek from Delaware River to Potato Hills Shoal. |Map shows soundings of Delaware River and Raccoon Creek. Also shows Raccoon Island.
